flowchart TD
    Start([Start Binary Search]) --> Input[Input: ISBN to find]
    Input --> Sort[Sort Book List<br/>by ISBN<br/>Ascending Order]
    Sort --> InitVars[Initialize:<br/>left = 0<br/>right = list size - 1]
    InitVars --> CheckLoop{left <= right?}

    CheckLoop -->|No| NotFound[Book Not Found<br/>Return null]
    CheckLoop -->|Yes| CalcMid[Calculate Middle:<br/>mid = left + right / 2]

    CalcMid --> GetMidBook[Get Book at<br/>index mid]
    GetMidBook --> GetMidISBN[Get ISBN of<br/>Middle Book]
    GetMidISBN --> Compare{Compare ISBNs}

    Compare -->|Equal| Found[Book Found!<br/>Return Book]
    Compare -->|Mid < Target| SearchRight[Target in Right Half<br/>Set left = mid + 1]
    Compare -->|Mid > Target| SearchLeft[Target in Left Half<br/>Set right = mid - 1]

    SearchRight --> CheckLoop
    SearchLeft --> CheckLoop

    Found --> End([End])
    NotFound --> End

